_header: Think that did his thee before
_description: ‘Quatuor precones ante diem Iudicii’ — two couplets

HerefordO414.Transcription:
Þenke þat ded his þe byfore& for þy sunne
                    þu myht boe loreþyn inggement wol boen fol strong&
                    þyn peyne wol boen fol long
